Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:19.80,Credits,,0,0,0,,[Ardent Spirits Keg]\NMain script from: Criminal Scans\NPreview TL: Rohupt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:23.90,Credits,,0,0,0,,[Ardent Spirits Keg]\NTiming/PR: validusername16\NStyling/Typesetting/TLC: Merlot-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:33.79,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Beika Town! Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.50,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Please watch your step when...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.29,DCMain,,0,0,0,,- No way!?\N- This is Beika Town, y'know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.94,DCMain,,0,0,0,,- Do you have a death wish!?\N‎- Get back in here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.87,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Ordinary folks don't even\Ncome close to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:42.87,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.63,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Because I'll be the one doing the killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.83,DCEpTitle,,0,0,0,,Along came a culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.81,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,That bastard is somewhere in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:03.40,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him! That's the reason I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.28,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,This ticket to Beika Town is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.90,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,A one-way ticket that leads to tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.55,DCMain,,0,0,0,,C'mon Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.57,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:12.24,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:15.04,DCMain,,0,0,0,,You dropped this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:16.04,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:17.25,DCMain,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.20,DCMain,,0,0,0,,That's hardly surprising in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.87,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Well then, once again,\Nthe one-way ticket to tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.59,DCMain,,0,0,0,,There's no opening to put the ticket in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.14,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Sir, the tickets go in through this gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:30.80,DCMain,,0,0,0,,T-They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.60,DCMain,,0,0,0,,That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:36.20,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko, you shouldn't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.41,DCMain,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.51,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if you get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.20,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.75,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,I don't have the luxury of murdering\Nsomeone over something so trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.07,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,You narrowly escaped death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.52,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,This is Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.42,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,The city of crimes that I admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.71,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,And the city I'll be living in starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.21,DCNarrationItalics,,0,0,0,,Their name is Hanzawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.21,DCNarrationItalics,,0,0,0,,And they're the culprit\Nof a crime that's yet to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.95,DCEpTitle,,0,0,0,,Continues in Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.68,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,First I need to find a place to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:17.18,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,I need to somehow find one at\Na rent of no more than 50,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.64,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,‎Eh!? 32,000 yen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.52,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,It has good natural lighting, a south-facing corner room,\Nit's just five years old, and even has separate toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.77,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,All of that for 32k!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.73,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,No, there has to be a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:31.32,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Such property couldn't exist for real,\Nit must be a customer-luring tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.91,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,And then when you go say,\N"I'd like to take a look at this"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:34.88,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.31,DCMain,,0,0,0,,You see, this one's been rented already,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.69,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I just forgot to take down the ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.66,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,At which point he'll go on to suggest\Na more expensive apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.20,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:46.75,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:51.05,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask about the apartment\Nadvertised at 32,000 yen outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:54.51,DCMain,,0,0,0,,It is still available, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.35,DCMain,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:55.97,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I-It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.35,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.14,DCMain,,0,0,0,,The landlord is a nice person as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:03.03,DCMain,,0,0,0,,and there's neither deposit\Nnor key money to be paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.98,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,To think that the initial cost\Nwould be this low!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.48,DCNarrationItalics,,0,0,0,,An instant property visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.53,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.10,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,‎No matter what, it's too cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.86,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's really filthy,\N‎or there could be a graveyard in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.07,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:15.91,DCMain,,0,0,0,,A condominium!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:16.96,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.16,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Such a great room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.16,DCMain,,0,0,0,,The scenery's also splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:24.02,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? The convenience store's nearby,\Nand it's only a three minute walk to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.00,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:28.84,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Erm, this apartment...\NIs there something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.63,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit too cheap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.38,DCMain,,0,0,0,,No, no, this is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.55,DCMain,,0,0,0,,For an exceedingly normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.34,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Stigmatized property, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.01,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Stigmatized property!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.35,DCMain,,0,0,0,,For example, it's in this spot that a golfer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:43.39,DCMain,,0,0,0,,struck and fatally wounded his\Nmodel girlfriend with a golf club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.02,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.44,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Here! There was a lot of blood in this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.73,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Don't point at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:53.82,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,I'll be planning that man's murder in\Nan apartment where an actual crime took place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.86,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,That's kinda scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.89,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I-I'd like to take a look at the\Nthe other options too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:00.37,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:03.81,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Inside a suitcase under\Nthe bed in this apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.95,DCMain,,0,0,0,,a corpse was found\Nin a tightly packed posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.58,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.63,DCMain,,0,0,0,,This is a bathroom in which\Na woman killed her younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:11.33,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll be able to shower in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.50,DCMain,,0,0,0,,And in here, as you can already see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.51,Beika Real Estate,,0,0,0,,"Beika Real Estate"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.13,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.51,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any apartments\Nwhich aren't stigmatized?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.48,DCMain,,0,0,0,,There are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:24.56,DCMain,,0,0,0,,A 4.5-{\i1}tatami{\i0} single room apartment constructed\Ntwenty years ago, wooden, and without a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.99,DCMain,,0,0,0,,The rent's 150k yen, plus deposit\Nand key money worth 3 months each!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.45,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Isn't this extremely strange!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.63,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I think you've got the wrong\Nend of the stick here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.11,DCMain,,0,0,0,,What place do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.74,DCMain,,0,0,0,,This is Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.94,Beika Town,,0,0,0,,Beika\NTown
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.95,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.83,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Crime-free apartments are extremely rare here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:45.12,DCMain,,0,0,0,,In the last twenty years, the number of\Nstigmatized properties has grown explosively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:49.54,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a conspiracy of sorts,\N‎or perhaps it's the work of a {\i1}shinigami{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:53.38,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Those of little means are left with no choice\Nbut to go with stigmatized property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.42,DCMain,,0,0,0,,That is the reality of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.95,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Listen up! I'm just giving\Nsome friendly advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.05,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Go back to the countryside, youngling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.27,DCMain,,0,0,0,,The apartment that we visited first,\NI'd like to once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.59,DCMain,,0,0,0,,It really is a great apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.64,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:13.10,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Yes, but for stigmatized property,\Ndon't you think that 32k's a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.32,DCMain,,0,0,0,,No, no... I can't make it any cheaper than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:20.19,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Then, with this, the rent should be reduced, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.32,DCNarrationItalics,,0,0,0,,Its value dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.70,DCMain,,0,0,0,,So, what's your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.51,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.76,DCNarrationItalics,,0,0,0,,His new life is still out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.60,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Omake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.58,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.60,Omake,,0,0,0,,Omake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.58,Where is he,,0,0,0,,Where is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.30,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,Beika Town really has a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:14.57,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,But somewhere in this city is that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.77,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,No matter where he hides,\NI'll definitely find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.82,DCItalic,,0,0,0,,And kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.78,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I saw Yoko-chan here the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.18,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Eh!? That idol, Okino Yoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.77,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Yup! She was shopping normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.90,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.93,DCMain,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.93,See you later,,0,0,0,,See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.18,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I, Hanzawa, whose both body\Nand soul are pitch black,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.87,DCMain,,0,0,0,,from Izumo, Shimane Prefecture,\Nhave come all the way to this town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.54,DCMain,,0,0,0,,which has the world's highest\Ncrime rate – Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.84,DCMain,,0,0,0,,That aside, I'm in big trouble all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.22,DCMain,,0,0,0,,I can't find a good apartment to lodge in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.79,DCMain,,0,0,0,,No matter where I go,\Nthe properties are stigmatized!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.80,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Just what the heck's up with this city!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.10,DCMain,,0,0,0,,But, however! I got a hint from\Nthe {\i1}onigiri{\i0}-faced brat who randomly passed by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.39,DCMain,,0,0,0,,So I came up with of a perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.80,DCMain,,0,0,0,,From here on, I can freely live my life of crime without having to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:55.34,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Encountering people is such a mysterious thing"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:09:00.96,DCPreviewTitle,,0,0,0,,Encountering people is such a mysterious thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.60,DCMain,,0,0,0,,And thanks for not being angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.69,DCMain,,0,0,0,,with the parodies being too overdone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.98,DCMain,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
